DefaultStartTime: The default start time for new level sequences, in seconds.
DefaultDuration: The default duration for new level sequences in seconds.
SubsequenceDirectory: The default directory for the subsequences.
ShotDirectory: The default directory for the shots.
SubsequencePrefix: The default prefix for subsequence names.
ShotPrefix: The default prefix for shot names.
ShotNumDigits: The number of digits for the shot number.
TakeNumDigits: The number of digits for the take number.
TakeSeparator: Character separator between the shot number and the take number.
FbxSettings: Mapping between fbx property name and property track path
